  "text": "The security of IoT systems is analyzed in [CITATION_1] - [CITATION_2] , in which the author discusses a specific smart home system and proposes a blockchain-based framework to guarantee security, confidentiality, integrity, and availability. The security issues for information and energy interactions in the cloud as well as edge formed by electric vehicle nodes have been raised in [CITATION_3] . A secure P2P data sharing system in vehicular computing networks by utilizing the concept of blockchain technologies is proposed in [CITATION_4] . A Mobi-Chain that applies blockchain technology to a novel m-commerce application to protect the security of data is investigated in [CITATION_5] , which concludes that blockchain technology is valid for future m-commerce security applications.",
